<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-61-1223 </DOCNO><TEXT>A brief report is given on the Greek experience of the two main reasonsfor firms failing to invest in energy efficiency. These are related topriorities and financial resources. In addition to encouraging new financingmethods such as third party finance, it is recommended that some kindof European Community guarantee should be introduced to cover specificprojects. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>